feat(5.2): embed widget — script loader + multi-snippet picker

New public/embed.js (vanilla, dependency-free, ~3KB) auto-mounts every
<div data-mkd-slidea="CODE"> with a lazy-loaded iframe. Listens for
"mkd-slidea-resize" postMessage from the embedded page (Embed.jsx
already emits it via ResizeObserver) and resizes the host iframe to
match content height.

Configurable via data-* attrs: height, radius, shadow, utm.
Validates the event-code regex; renders an inline error if invalid.
Idempotent (guards against double load); exposes window.MKDSlidea.mount()
for SPAs that inject markers after initial load.

Host settings: replaced the single iframe textarea with a 3-tab snippet
picker (iFrame / Script / WordPress shortcode) + copy-to-clipboard with
"Копирано!" feedback. All embeds now carry UTM tracking
(utm_source=embed, utm_medium=iframe|widget) for growth attribution.

Build: Host 34.20KB gzip (+0.50KB). Zero new deps.
